snippet.title: True Crime Paranormal with Eve EP
snippet.description:
This channel is dedicated to missing persons cases, true crime and discussions regarding such cases. It will also include paranormal and spiritual talk regarding any and all cases we discuss. This channel is about using any and all means to help find missing persons cases, or discuss opinions and the facts related to such. No one should discriminate against anyone’s beliefs, and we shall maintain dignity for those who are missing, passed on as well as their families. This channel will use and discuss cases with logic, reasoning, opinions, and open discussion. We will also use paranormal equipment such as EVP, voice recordings and multiple other means. I will personally be using Tarot as well as said equipment to obtain any information spirit or spirits want to communicate. 

This channel is for entertainment purposes only.
